186
00:12:06,087 --> 00:12:09,531
of brain function 
and their link to behavior.

187
00:12:10,900 --> 00:12:15,059
As a cautionary note, I think
it's important to consider the limitations

188
00:12:15,059 --> 00:12:16,832
