194
00:12:40,191 --> 00:12:43,984
more and more detailed measurements
and perturbations.

195
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:50,419
Here we've begun to think
about how we might put together

196
00:12:50,419 --> 00:12:55,971
our biophysical knowledge
